doc.after: Like several other large tyrannosaurids Tarbosaurus is known from relatively abundant and well preserved fossil material In fact one quarter of all fossils collected from the Nemegt Formation belong to Tarbosaurus 31 Although Tarbosaurus has not been studied as thoroughly as the North American tyrannosaurids 5 the available material has allowed scientists to draw limited conclusions about its biology
